casebody.data:
Michael HOLBROOK
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided May 15, 2019 Vishal K. Garg, assigned counsel, in support of the petition. C. Robert Satti, Jr., supervisory assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Michael Holbrook's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 189 Conn. App. 108 , 206 A.3d 246 (2019), is denied.
